  "detailed_description": "HOW FAR WILL YOU GO TO SAVE YOUR ONLY DAUGHTER'S LIFE?<br><br>Is there a limit?<br><br>Help Owen Wright rescue his daughter from the clutches of the Lonely Hearts Killer, the mysterious figure who kidnaps and murders people who have suffered a love gone wrong.<br><br>Unravel the intrigue and put a stop to the whirlwind of crime that has paralyzed this late 19th century British city.<br><br>The killer must be stopped so justice can be done!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover the clues!<br></li><li>Amazing Hidden Object game-play, tricky puzzles and mini-games.<br></li><li>Explore a 19th century English city, amazing Victorian homes and meet an intriguing cast of characters!<br></li><li>Stop a demented mind and end the killing spree!<br></li><li>Save Olivia before it's too late!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Collector's Edition includes;</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A bonus chapter with a surprising plot<br></li><li>An integrated strategy guide<br></li><li>Downloadable soundtrack, concept art and wallpapers<br></li><li>An interview with the developers</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "HOW FAR WILL YOU GO TO SAVE YOUR ONLY DAUGHTER'S LIFE?<br><br>Is there a limit?<br><br>Help Owen Wright rescue his daughter from the clutches of the Lonely Hearts Killer, the mysterious figure who kidnaps and murders people who have suffered a love gone wrong.<br><br>Unravel the intrigue and put a stop to the whirlwind of crime that has paralyzed this late 19th century British city.<br><br>The killer must be stopped so justice can be done!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover the clues!<br></li><li>Amazing Hidden Object game-play, tricky puzzles and mini-games.<br></li><li>Explore a 19th century English city, amazing Victorian homes and meet an intriguing cast of characters!<br></li><li>Stop a demented mind and end the killing spree!<br></li><li>Save Olivia before it's too late!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Collector's Edition includes;</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A bonus chapter with a surprising plot<br></li><li>An integrated strategy guide<br></li><li>Downloadable soundtrack, concept art and wallpapers<br></li><li>An interview with the developers</li></ul>",
